msgctxt "sn55.44:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Sagāthakapuññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "5. Overflowing Merit, With Verses "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 44. Paṭhamamahaddhanasutta → aḍḍhasuttaṃ (bj) | mahaddhana or aḍḍha 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Paṭhamamahaddhanasutta "
msgstr "44. Rich (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: mahaddhano → mahaḍḍhano (bj)
#. VAR: mahābhogo’ti → mahābhogo mahāyasoti (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn55.44:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a noble disciple who has four things is said to be rich, affluent, and wealthy. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.44:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.4"
msgid "dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.7"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is said to be rich, affluent, and wealthy.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.44:2.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

